es pada data target (`Close`) dengan plot 4 komponen: Observed, Trend, Seasonal, Residual.","metadata":{}},{"id":"454d89f7-506c-4629-a827-4456359264b5","cell_type":"code","source":"close_series = df.set_index('Date')['Close']\n\ndecomp_data = close_series.iloc[:8760] if len(close_series) > 8760 else close_series\n\ndecomposition = seasonal_decompose(\n    decomp_data, model='additive', period=24, extrapolate_trend='freq'\n)\n\nfig, axes = plt.subplots(4, 1, figsize=(16, 12))\npairs = [\n    (decomp_data,           'Observed',  '#2196F3'),\n    (decomposition.trend,   'Trend',     '#FF9800'),\n    (decomposition.seasonal,'Seasonal',  '#4CAF50'),\n    (decomposition.resid,   'Residual',  '#F44336'),\n]\nfor ax, (data, label, c) in zip(axes, pairs):\n    ax.plot(data.index, data.values, color=c, linewidth=0.9)\n    ax.set_title(label, fontweight='bold', fontsize=12)\n    ax.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n\nplt.suptitle('Dekomposisi Time Series — Bitcoin Close (Period=24h)',\n             fontsize=14, fontweight='bold')\nplt.tight_layout()\nplt.show()","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-06-02T04:16:01.916944Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-06-02T04:16:01.917336Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-06-02T04:16:02.778051Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-06-02T04:16:01.917295Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-06-02T04:16:02.777118Z"}},"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"<Figure size 1600x1200 with 4 Axes>","image/png":"\n"},"metadata":{}}],"execution_count":6},{"id":"b1640254-3a55-4aa3-933a-4c771a232024","cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 4. Analisis ACF & PACF","metadata":{}},{"id":"3b0db1da-03fe-4327-8db8-d681905501ec","cell_type":"markdown","source":"Window size ditentukan berdasarkan hasil uji ACF & PACF. Dari plot terlihat autokorelasi signifikan hingga lag ~48 → `WINDOW_SIZE = 48`.","metadata":{}},{"id":"75829524-3a28-42fb-8cbb-0a65e78669d7","cell_type":"code","source":"acf_data = close_series.diff().dropna().iloc[:5000]\n\nfi