ta":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"\u001b[1m Total params: \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;34m310,913\u001b[0m (1.19 MB)\n","text/html":"<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> Total params: </span><span style=\"color: #00af00; text-decoration-color: #00af00\">310,913</span> (1.19 MB)\n</pre>\n"},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"\u001b[1m Trainable params: \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;34m310,913\u001b[0m (1.19 MB)\n","text/html":"<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> Trainable params: </span><span style=\"color: #00af00; text-decoration-color: #00af00\">310,913</span> (1.19 MB)\n</pre>\n"},"metadata":{}},{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/plain":"\u001b[1m Non-trainable params: \u001b[0m\u001b[38;5;34m0\u001b[0m (0.00 B)\n","text/html":"<pre style=\"white-space:pre;overflow-x:auto;line-height:normal;font-family:Menlo,'DejaVu Sans Mono',consolas,'Courier New',monospace\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold\"> Non-trainable params: </span><span style=\"color: #00af00; text-decoration-color: #00af00\">0</span> (0.00 B)\n</pre>\n"},"metadata":{}},{"name":"stdout","text":"Seq2Seq LSTM (Subclassing) siap\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":18},{"id":"aeaf2b27-88ff-46ca-ad77-430955f5bf46","cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 10. Custom Loss & Custom Callback","metadata":{}},{"id":"ede97853-a703-4455-88af-f02ba49e83c3","cell_type":"markdown","source":"* `custom_mae_loss` — fungsi MAE dibangun dari nol.  \n* `CustomEarlyStopping` — callback early stopping dari nol.  \n* `WeightedHorizonMAE` — custom loss dengan bobot lebih besar pada horizon yang lebih jauh (step 1 = 1.0 → step 24 = 2.0).  \n* `CustomReduceLROnPlateau` — callback yang mengurangi learning rate saat val loss stagnan.","metadata":{}},{"id":"21452f21-b461-4e8d-a386-139b41712305","cell_type":"code","source":"# Custom Loss 1 : MAE dari Nol\ndef custom_mae_loss(y_true, y_pred):\n    \"\"\"Mean Absolute Error diimplementasi dari nol.\"\"\"\n    return tf.reduce_mean(tf.abs(y_true - y_pred))\n\n# Custom Loss 2 : Weighted Horizon MAE\nclass WeightedHorizonMAE:\n    def __init__(self, horizon, weight_scale=1.0):\n        weights = [1.0 + (i / horizon) * weight_scale for i in range(horizon)]\n        self.weights = tf.constant(weights, dtype=tf.float32)\n        w_str = ', '.join([f'step{i+1}={w:.2f}' for i, w in enumerate(weights[:3])])\n        print(f'WeightedHorizonMAE: {w_str} ... step{horizon}={weights[-1]:.2f}')\n\n    def __call__(self, y_true, y_pred):\n        abs_err = tf.abs(y_true - y_pred)        # (batch, horizon)\n        return tf.reduce_mean(abs_err * self.weights)\n\nweighted_loss = WeightedHorizonMAE(horizon=HORIZON, weight_scale=1.0)\nprint('Custom Loss OK')","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.737254Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.737566Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.746436Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.737527Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.745776Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"WeightedHorizonMAE: step1=1.00, step2=1.04, step3=1.08 ... step24=1.96\nCustom Loss OK\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":19},{"id":"8f777c60-104a-49ae-975f-e6aa7165d1ba","cell_type":"code","source":"# Custom Callback 1 : Early Stopping dari Nol\nclass CustomEarlyStopping:\n    \"\"\"Berhenti training jika val_loss tidak membaik selama `patience` epoch.\"\"\"\n    def __init__(self, patience=5, min_delta=1e-5):\n        self.patience  = patience\n        self.min_delta = min_delta\n        self.best      = np.inf\n        self.counter   = 0\n        self.stop      = False\n\n    def __call__(self, val_loss):\n        if val_loss < self.best - self.min_delta:\n            self.best    = val_loss\n            self.counter = 0\n        else:\n            self.counter += 1\n            if self.counter >= self.patience:\n                self.stop = True\n        return self.stop\n\n\n# Custom Callback 2 : Reduce LR on Plateau dari Nol\nclass CustomReduceLROnPlateau:\n    \"\"\"Kurangi LR jika val_loss stagnan selama `patience` epoch.\"\"\"\n    def __init__(self, optimizer, patience=3, factor=0.5, min_lr=1e-6):\n        self.optimizer = optimizer\n        self.patience  = patience\n        self.factor    = factor\n        self.min_lr    = min_lr\n        self.best      = np.inf\n        self.counter   = 0\n\n    def __call__(self, val_loss):\n        if val_loss < self.best - 1e-5:\n            self.best    = val_loss\n            self.counter = 0\n        else:\n            self.counter += 1\n            if self.counter >= self.patience:\n                old_lr = float(self.optimizer.learning_rate)\n                new_lr = max(old_lr * self.factor, self.min_lr)\n                self.optimizer.learning_rate.assign(new_lr)\n                print(f'    ReduceLR: {old_lr:.2e} → {new_lr:.2e}')\n                self.counter = 0\n\nprint('Custom Callbacks OK')","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.747418Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.747720Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.766879Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.747697Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.766068Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"Custom Callbacks OK\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":20},{"id":"daba391c-dd38-4d8b-b88a-0681298f8415","cell_type":"markdown","source":"## 11. Custom Training Loop (tf.GradientTape)","metadata":{}},{"id":"99bcda47-7ca9-4a5a-9697-1409d91b04b8","cell_type":"markdown","source":"Custom Training Loop menggunakan `tf.GradientTape`. Menampilkan epoch, loss, MAE, val loss, dan val MAE setiap epoch.","metadata":{}},{"id":"609d2c12-85c4-47a5-86e4-2ba6e03df694","cell_type":"code","source":"def make_decoder_input(batch_y):\n    \"\"\"Buat decoder input dengan teacher forcing: geser target 1 step ke kanan.\"\"\"\n    bos    = tf.zeros((tf.shape(batch_y)[0], 1, 1), dtype=tf.float32)\n    target = tf.expand_dims(batch_y[:, :-1], axis=-1)  # (batch, horizon-1, 1)\n    return tf.concat([bos, target], axis=1)             # (batch, horizon, 1)\n\n\ndef custom_train_loop(model, train_ds, val_ds, optimizer, loss_fn,\n                      epochs=30, patience_es=7, patience_lr=3,\n                      is_seq2seq=False, model_name='Model'):\n    early_stop = CustomEarlyStopping(patience=patience_es)\n    reduce_lr  = CustomReduceLROnPlateau(optimizer, patience=patience_lr)\n    history    = {'loss': [], 'val_loss': [], 'mae': [], 'val_mae': []}\n\n    print(f'\\n{\"=\"*74}')\n    print(f'  Training: {model_name}')\n    print(f'{\"=\"*74}')\n    print(f'  {\"Epoch\":>5} | {\"Loss\":>10} | {\"MAE\":>10} | {\"Val Loss\":>10} | {\"Val MAE\":>10}')\n    print(f'  {\"-\"*5}-+-{\"-\"*10}-+-{\"-\"*10}-+-{\"-\"*10}-+-{\"-\"*10}')\n\n    for epoch in range(1, epochs + 1):\n\n        # Train\n        train_losses, train_maes = [], []\n        for batch_X, batch_y in train_ds:\n            with tf.GradientTape() as tape:\n                if is_seq2seq:\n                    dec_in = make_decoder_input(batch_y)\n                    preds  = model((batch_X, dec_in), training=True)\n                else:\n                    preds  = model(batch_X, training=True)\n                loss = loss_fn(batch_y, preds)\n\n            grads = tape.gradient(loss, model.trainable_variables)\n            optimizer.apply_gradients(zip(grads, model.trainable_variables))\n            train_losses.append(float(loss))\n            train_maes.append(float(custom_mae_loss(batch_y, preds)))\n\n        # Validation\n        val_losses, val_maes = [], []\n        for batch_X, batch_y in val_ds:\n            if is_seq2seq:\n                dec_in = make_decoder_input(batch_y)\n                preds  = model((batch_X, dec_in), training=False)\n            else:\n                preds  = model(batch_X, training=False)\n            val_losses.append(float(loss_fn(batch_y, preds)))\n            val_maes.append(float(custom_mae_loss(batch_y, preds)))\n\n        ep_loss     = np.mean(train_losses)\n        ep_mae      = np.mean(train_maes)\n        ep_val_loss = np.mean(val_losses)\n        ep_val_mae  = np.mean(val_maes)\n\n        history['loss'].append(ep_loss)\n        history['mae'].append(ep_mae)\n        history['val_loss'].append(ep_val_loss)\n        history['val_mae'].append(ep_val_mae)\n\n        print(f'  {epoch:>5} | {ep_loss:>10.6f} | {ep_mae:>10.6f} | {ep_val_loss:>10.6f} | {ep_val_mae:>10.6f}')\n\n        reduce_lr(ep_val_loss)\n        if early_stop(ep_val_loss):\n            print(f'  Early stopping pada epoch {epoch}')\n            break\n\n    print(f'{\"=\"*74}')\n    return history\n\nprint('Custom training loop OK')","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.767880Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.768626Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.785862Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.768601Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.784985Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"Custom training loop OK\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":21},{"id":"9cb52daa-648f-4731-9003-f46264c2d65d","cell_type":"code","source":"EPOCHS = 30\nLR     = 1e-3\n\nopt_baseline = keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=LR)\nopt_seq2seq  = keras.optimizers.Adam(learning_rate=LR)","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.786552Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.786831Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.809312Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.786798Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-06-02T04:16:10.808763Z"}},"outputs":[],"execution_count":22},{"id":"5